{
  "stem": "26728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would pull this rope with this man-- now this is by his arms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want to-- his, his arms would be back here, and then it would be connected to this rope, which they would pull the pulley.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Would pull his arms clear out of the sockets usually, and pull him up six or seven feet on this post and just let him hang there five, six, eight hours.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Never give him any water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there'd be, you know, 10 or 15 posts like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if any infraction of any kind, or just because I decided, OK, put him up on the post.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's how it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Total, absolute power.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Total absolute helplessness.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this is when you see-- when you-- when you have time to contemplate this or talk about this with someone else, that's when you get angry.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's when you say, you know-- and you use bad language.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got to get back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, God damn it, if we get a chance-- if we get back in combat-- see, now we're still talking about April.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We've didn't know when the war was-- we wanted to get back so bad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We remembered, a couple of us that, that were in that shoot-- that turkey shoot in, in Belgium, we wanted to do that so bad, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Remember I told you I had felt a little bit guilty about this thing, and it was kind of an abstract thing?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I relived that over and over, and it just got off on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It made me feel good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "God damn, I wish I had a chance to do that a whole bunch of times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's how-- you know-- just kill those bastards for what they had done to these people.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
